data.description: This gorgeous home with 3 bedrooms and 2 baths, has a stunning kitchen, wide open spaces to work in while entertaining family and friends. Beautiful stone archway has been recently added, there's new hardwood flooring, the basement has been renovated and now offers a bar and workout room. Owners will include some furniture, if desired, to include some dressers and living room furniture. A new oven has just been installed as well! The master suite is to die for! It offers a whirlpool tub and classy cabinetry. Central air, composite wraparound deck, blacktop driveway, and new landscaping beautifies the country setting, to include a front garden that's in full bloom.You're going to be so comfortable living here, you'll never want to leave... This home is one not to miss!
